column3: What is the number of Immigration Enforcement visits conducted in each London postcode area (E, EC, N, NW, SE, SW, W, WC) in 2022? Split data by postcode district.
Table 1 - Number of Immigration Enforcement visits conducted in each London postcode area (E, EC, N, NW, SE, SW, W, WC) in 2022
These figures have been taken from a live operational database. As such, numbers may change as information on that system is updated.
Data extracted on 04/05/2023 from OAR1 PRAU On Demand report.
Data covers the following period: 01 January 2022 to 31 December 2022.
If this data is to be shared externally, in order to protect individual identification, any count that is less than 5 should be replaced with "<5" and any Totals columns/rows should be removed
